data.description: VA ASSUMABLE LOAN AT 2.75%!!! Seller is also offering 2-1 BUY DOWN! Welcome to this charming 4/3 bath home, nestled in a serene  neighborhood. Home is MOVE IN READY for the next buyers. The split floor plan provides both privacy and spaciousness. You will love this great room with HIGH VAULTED ceilings, FIREPLACE, Sliding glass doors for backyard and it also opens up into the massive FLORIDA ROOM/Bonus Room. One of the highlights of this home is the open layout, which connects the living, dining, and kitchen areas. This delightful Chefs kitchen boasts brand new appliances, Fabulous Top of the line GRANITE countertops, Pantry, Tiled BACKSPLASH and High Vaulted ceilings. You'll have everything you need to enjoy gathering time. Washer and dryer included eliminating the need for an extra chore of appliance shopping. You can move in and start enjoying your new home right away. Master bedroom suite is massive featuring Dual Sinks, WALK IN CLOSETS, Stand up shower and soaking bath tub. All the bedrooms are very nice size  and provide lots of windows and lighted ceiling fans. Step outside, and you'll find an oasis awaiting you in the backyard. An above-ground pool, encircled by decking, provides the perfect spot for relaxation and soaking up the sun on warm summer days. Imagine hosting poolside barbecues, lounging with friends, or enjoying a morning coffee on your private deck. Several recent upgrades enhance this home, including a new roof, water heater, carpeting, and a freshly installed fence for added privacy and security. The deck, constructed in July 2023, offers an extended outdoor living space where you can bask in the beauty of your surroundings. This backyard making it an ideal backdrop for relaxation and outdoor activities. HOME HAS SOLAR PANELS SO THERE IS ALMOST NO ELECTRIC BILL! Located minutes to Navy Federal, I10, Restaurants and only 20 minutes from downtown Pensacola, NAS and lovely WHITE SAND Beaches. Call for your private showing today!
